Y easy to get.  Load up DE illusion and goto the Caves in EFP and find a DE there talk to her and get a letter you bring back to the cleric guild and hand in.  I'd say 10 round trips would get you to the point where you could walk in the cleric guild as a ally without illusion.  I went to dubious with just 1 letter.  &quot;The Dead&quot; is the hard faction to raise.<br>
