Tizla <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulannellavelglarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lannella Velglarn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/leaf.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/7/02 2:02:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4861.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate book</span><hr size=1> Which quest is it?  I looked on Alla's and found only this:<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/qsearch.html?faction=81">everquest.allakhazam.com/...faction=81</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END-->  None of which seem to be centered around FP.  Can you give the link for the quest? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaanmage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aanmage</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/7/02 9:14:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4861.topic&index=15>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hate book</span><hr size=1> OK Tizla, here are a few questions I have regarding the quest in EFP and its relation to fetching Hate book:<br>
<br>
1) Can you detail where the EFP NPC is? Is it the female inkie outside by shoreline?<br>
<br>
2) Does raising DE cleric faction (Priests of Innoruuk) have any effect in Hate, where the faction of 1st floor is Inhabitants of Hate? (2nd floor being KOS to anyone regardless of faction).<br>
<br>
3) From your post, it seems as if you neutralized the &quot;everyone is KOS in PoH&quot; thing and I am curious as to what the 1st floor mobs conned while skulking and/or visible?<br>
<br>
